Height vs Nodes
Minimum nodes = 2 Maximum = 3 for Height = 1
Minimum nodes = 3 Maximum = 7 for Height = 2
Minimum Nodes = (n+1)
Maximum Nodes = (2^(h+1)) - 1 (Forms a GP)
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Minimum height = 1 Maximum = 2 for Nodes = 3
Minimum height = 2 Maximum = 6 for Nodes = 7
Maximum Height = (n-1)
Minimum Height = [log{base 2}(n+1)]-1
